name: Carbon Copy #17 - Jack Huston Cover (Print)
description: This is the PRINT edition, you can also download the issue instantly from the ZINE stand for £2.50 For our 17th issue, British actor Jack Huston poses on top of a McLaren 12C Spider sports car, whilst being photographed by legendary Rock 'n' Roll photographer Mick Rock. This luxury soft-back in colour and b/w features 224 pages of fashion editorials plus interviews. The front cover story with Jack Huston dominates with a 20-page spread, photographed in New York whilst the back cover is none other than male supermodel Garrett Neff, photographed by celebrated photographer Yu Tsai. We feature interviews with both Jack and Garrett.
